 \hspace{-1cm}\small\begin{bmatrix}I_n&A/\sqrt{\lambda}\\0&I_m\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\lambda I_n-AB&0\\\sqrt{\lambda}B&\lambda I_m\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}\lambda I_n&\sqrt{\lambda}A\\\sqrt{\lambda}B&\lambda I_m\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}I_n&0\\B/\sqrt{\lambda}&I_m\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}\lambda I_n&\sqrt{\lambda}A\\0&\lambda I_m-BA\end{bmatrix}\tag{2} 
